          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total gamma-ray yield was obtained by",
                "summing the cross sections of 0.332 (21-Na), 0.351,",
                "1.395 (21-Ne), 0.937 (18-F), 1.634 (20-Ne), and",
                "1.121, 5.270 + 5.299 (15-N) MeV gamma-rays.",
                " The total fusion cross sections were obtained from",
                "the total gamma-ray cross sections, dividing the",
                "latter by the correction factor Fg, as described",
                "in ref.(see REL-REF).",
                "The anisotropy of the angular distribution of the",
                "gamma rays used in the determination of fusion cross",
                "section was investigated, and was found to be",
                "negligible."
              ]
            }
          ],
